  "prompt": "What is the average price for a desktop computer?",
  "response": "The average price for a desktop computer can vary widely depending on the specifications, brand, and features. As of recent years, you can expect to find budget desktop computers in the range of $300 to $600. Mid-range desktops typically cost between $600 and $1,200, while high-end gaming or professional workstations can range from $1,200 to several thousand dollars.\n\nTo get a more accurate and updated average price, it is best to check current prices from various retailers such as Amazon, Best Buy, Newegg, and manufacturer websites like Dell, HP, and Lenovo.",
